Description: The purpose of this guide is to coordinate the data science
    efforts of the Rock Island District of the U.S. Army Corps of
    Engineers. We have established these best practice guidelines to
    streamline onboarding of new data scientists, promote consistency
    across projects, and ensure the quality and reproducibility of our
    work.
